// ============non-terminal types=============
//  # => Integer
//  <assign> => Statement
//  <class decl> => ClassDecl
//  <class decl>+ => List<ClassDecl>
//  <decl in class> => Decl
//  <decl in class>* => List<Decl>
//  <empty bracket pair> => Object
//  <exp1> => Exp
//  <exp2> => Exp
//  <exp3> => Exp
//  <exp4> => Exp
//  <exp5> => Exp
//  <exp> => Exp
//  <inst var decl> => Decl
//  <local var decl> => Statement
//  <method decl> => Decl
//  <program> => Program
//  <start> => void
//  <stmt> => Statement
//  <stmt>* => List<Statement>
//  <type> => Type
//  CHARLIT => Integer
//  ID => String
//  INTLIT => Integer
//  STRINGLIT => String
//  `! => void
//  `!= => void
//  `% => void
//  `&& => void
//  `( => void
//  `) => void
//  `* => void
//  `+ => void
//  `++ => void
//  `, => void
//  `- => void
//  `-- => void
//  `. => void
//  `/ => void
//  `: => void
//  `; => void
//  `< => void
//  `<= => void
//  `= => void
//  `== => void
//  `> => void
//  `>= => void
//  `[ => void
//  `] => void
//  `abstract => void
//  `assert => void
//  `boolean => void
//  `break => void
//  `byte => void
//  `case => void
//  `catch => void
//  `char => void
//  `class => void
//  `const => void
//  `continue => void
//  `default => void
//  `do => void
//  `double => void
//  `else => void
//  `enum => void
//  `extends => void
//  `false => void
//  `final => void
//  `finally => void
//  `float => void
//  `for => void
//  `goto => void
//  `if => void
//  `implements => void
//  `import => void
//  `instanceof => void
//  `int => void
//  `interface => void
//  `long => void
//  `native => void
//  `new => void
//  `null => void
//  `package => void
//  `private => void
//  `protected => void
//  `public => void
//  `return => void
//  `short => void
//  `static => void
//  `strictfp => void
//  `super => void
//  `switch => void
//  `synchronized => void
//  `this => void
//  `throw => void
//  `throws => void
//  `transient => void
//  `true => void
//  `try => void
//  `void => void
//  `volatile => void
//  `while => void
//  `{ => void
//  `|| => void
//  `} => void
//  any => Character
//  any* => List<Character>
//  any128 => Character
//  digit => Character
//  digit* => List<Character>
//  digit128 => Character
//  hexDigit => Character
//  hexDigit* => List<Character>
//  hexDigit128 => Character
//  idChar => Character
//  idChar* => List<Character>
//  idChar128 => Character
//  letter => Character
//  letter128 => Character
//  registerNewline => void
//  ws => void
//  ws* => void
// ============productions (after empty-removal)=============
// 0: $$start ::= <start>
// 1: <start> ::= ws* <program>
// 2: <start> ::= <program>
// 3: <program> ::= <class decl>+
// 4: <class decl> ::= `class ID `{ <decl in class>* `}
// 5: <class decl> ::= `class ID `{ `}
// 6: <class decl> ::= `class ID `extends ID `{ <decl in class>* `}
// 7: <class decl> ::= `class ID `extends ID `{ `}
// 8: <decl in class> ::= <method decl>
// 9: <method decl> ::= `public `void ID `( `) `{ <stmt>* `}
// 10: <method decl> ::= `public `void ID `( `) `{ `}
// 11: <type> ::= `int
// 12: <type> ::= `boolean
// 13: <type> ::= `void
// 14: <type> ::= `null
// 15: <type> ::= ID
// 16: <type> ::= <type> <empty bracket pair>
// 17: <empty bracket pair> ::= `[ `]
// 18: <stmt> ::= `{ <stmt>* `}
// 19: <stmt> ::= `{ `}
// 20: <stmt> ::= <assign> `;
// 21: <stmt> ::= <local var decl> `;
// 22: <stmt> ::= `if `( <exp> `) <stmt> !`else
// 23: <stmt> ::= `if `( <exp> `) <stmt> `else <stmt>
// 24: <stmt> ::= `while `( <exp> `) <stmt>
// 25: <stmt> ::= `break `;
// 26: <assign> ::= <exp> `= <exp>
// 27: <local var decl> ::= <type> ID `= <exp>
// 28: <exp> ::= <exp5>
// 29: <exp5> ::= <exp4>
// 30: <exp4> ::= <exp3>
// 31: <exp3> ::= <exp2>
// 32: <exp2> ::= <exp1>
// 33: <exp5> ::= <exp5> `< <exp4>
// 34: <exp5> ::= <exp5> `<= <exp4>
// 35: <exp5> ::= <exp5> `> <exp4>
// 36: <exp4> ::= <exp4> `+ <exp3>
// 37: <exp4> ::= <exp4> `- <exp3>
// 38: <exp3> ::= <exp3> `* <exp2>
// 39: <exp3> ::= <exp3> `/ <exp2>
// 40: <exp3> ::= <exp3> `% <exp2>
// 41: <exp2> ::= `( <type> `) <exp1>
// 42: <exp2> ::= `+ <exp1>
// 43: <exp2> ::= `- <exp1>
// 44: <exp2> ::= `! <exp1>
// 45: <exp1> ::= ID
// 46: <exp1> ::= <exp1> !<empty bracket pair> `[ <exp> `]
// 47: <exp1> ::= INTLIT
// 48: <exp1> ::= STRINGLIT
// 49: <exp1> ::= CHARLIT
// 50: <exp1> ::= `this
// 51: <exp1> ::= `true
// 52: <exp1> ::= `false
// 53: <exp1> ::= `null
// 54: letter ::= {"A".."Z" "a".."z"}
// 55: letter128 ::= {193..218 225..250}
// 56: digit ::= {"0".."9"}
// 57: digit128 ::= {176..185}
// 58: any ::= {0..127}
// 59: any128 ::= {128..255}
// 60: ws ::= " "
// 61: ws ::= {10}
// 62: `boolean ::= "#" "b" "o" ws*
// 63: `boolean ::= "#" "b" "o"
// 64: `class ::= "#" "c" "l" ws*
// 65: `class ::= "#" "c" "l"
// 66: `extends ::= "#" "e" "x" ws*
// 67: `extends ::= "#" "e" "x"
// 68: `void ::= "#" "v" "o" ws*
// 69: `void ::= "#" "v" "o"
// 70: `int ::= "#" "i" "t" ws*
// 71: `int ::= "#" "i" "t"
// 72: `while ::= "#" "w" "h" ws*
// 73: `while ::= "#" "w" "h"
// 74: `if ::= "#" "+" ws*
// 75: `if ::= "#" "+"
// 76: `else ::= "#" "e" "l" ws*
// 77: `else ::= "#" "e" "l"
// 78: `break ::= "#" "b" "r" ws*
// 79: `break ::= "#" "b" "r"
// 80: `this ::= "#" "t" "h" ws*
// 81: `this ::= "#" "t" "h"
// 82: `false ::= "#" "f" "a" ws*
// 83: `false ::= "#" "f" "a"
// 84: `true ::= "#" "t" "r" ws*
// 85: `true ::= "#" "t" "r"
// 86: `null ::= "#" "n" "u" ws*
// 87: `null ::= "#" "n" "u"
// 88: `public ::= "#" "p" "u" ws*
// 89: `public ::= "#" "p" "u"
// 90: `! ::= "!" ws*
// 91: `! ::= "!"
// 92: `% ::= "%" ws*
// 93: `% ::= "%"
// 94: `* ::= "*" ws*
// 95: `* ::= "*"
// 96: `( ::= "(" ws*
// 97: `( ::= "("
// 98: `) ::= ")" ws*
// 99: `) ::= ")"
// 100: `{ ::= "{" ws*
// 101: `{ ::= "{"
// 102: `} ::= "}" ws*
// 103: `} ::= "}"
// 104: `- ::= "-" ws*
// 105: `- ::= "-"
// 106: `+ ::= "+" ws*
// 107: `+ ::= "+"
// 108: `= ::= "=" ws*
// 109: `= ::= "="
// 110: `[ ::= "[" ws*
// 111: `[ ::= "["
// 112: `] ::= "]" ws*
// 113: `] ::= "]"
// 114: `< ::= "<" ws*
// 115: `< ::= "<"
// 116: `<= ::= "@" "<" ws*
// 117: `<= ::= "@" "<"
// 118: `> ::= ">" !"=" ws*
// 119: `> ::= ">" !"="
// 120: `; ::= ";" ws*
// 121: `; ::= ";"
// 122: `/ ::= "/" ws*
// 123: `/ ::= "/"
// 124: ID ::= letter128 ws*
// 125: ID ::= letter128
// 126: ID ::= letter idChar* $$0
// 127: ID ::= letter $$0
// 128: INTLIT ::= {"1".."9"} digit* $$1
// 129: INTLIT ::= {"1".."9"} $$1
// 130: INTLIT ::= digit128 ws*
// 131: INTLIT ::= digit128
// 132: INTLIT ::= "0" hexDigit* $$2
// 133: INTLIT ::= "0" $$2
// 134: STRINGLIT ::= "@" '"' ws*
// 135: STRINGLIT ::= "@" '"'
// 136: STRINGLIT ::= '"' any* $$3
// 137: STRINGLIT ::= '"' $$3
// 138: CHARLIT ::= "'" any ws*
// 139: CHARLIT ::= "'" any
// 140: idChar ::= letter
// 141: idChar ::= digit
// 142: idChar ::= "_"
// 143: idChar128 ::= letter128
// 144: idChar128 ::= digit128
// 145: idChar128 ::= {223}
// 146: hexDigit ::= {"0".."9" "A".."Z" "a".."z"}
// 147: hexDigit128 ::= {176..185 193..198 225..230}
// 148: digit* ::= digit* digit
// 149: digit* ::= digit
// 150: any* ::= any* any
// 151: any* ::= any
// 152: <decl in class>* ::= <decl in class>* <decl in class>
// 153: <decl in class>* ::= <decl in class>
// 154: hexDigit* ::= hexDigit* hexDigit
// 155: hexDigit* ::= hexDigit
// 156: <stmt>* ::= <stmt>* <stmt>
// 157: <stmt>* ::= <stmt>
// 158: idChar* ::= idChar* idChar
// 159: idChar* ::= idChar
// 160: <class decl>+ ::= <class decl>
// 161: <class decl>+ ::= <class decl>+ <class decl>
// 162: ws* ::= ws* ws
// 163: ws* ::= ws
// 164: $$0 ::= idChar128 ws*
// 165: $$0 ::= idChar128
// 166: $$1 ::= digit128 ws*
// 167: $$1 ::= digit128
// 168: $$2 ::= hexDigit128 ws*
// 169: $$2 ::= hexDigit128
// 170: $$3 ::= any128 ws*
// 171: $$3 ::= any128
// =================symbols=======================
// 0: $$start

**** STATE 0 ****
    $$start ::= <%> <start> // $
    -----------------------
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `extends ID `{ <decl in class>* `} // $
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `extends ID `{ <decl in class>* `} // <class decl>
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `extends ID `{ [<decl in class>*] `} // $
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `extends ID `{ [<decl in class>*] `} // <class decl>
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `{ <decl in class>* `} // $
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `{ <decl in class>* `} // <class decl>
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `{ [<decl in class>*] `} // $
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `{ [<decl in class>*] `} // <class decl>
    <class decl>+ ::= <%> <class decl> // $
    <class decl>+ ::= <%> <class decl> // <class decl>
    <class decl>+ ::= <%> <class decl>+ <class decl> // $
    <class decl>+ ::= <%> <class decl>+ <class decl> // <class decl>
    <program> ::= [#] <%> <class decl>+ // $
    <start> ::= <%> ws* <program> // $
    <start> ::= [ws*] <%> <program> // $
    `class ::= <%> "#" "c" "l" [ws*] // ID
    `class ::= <%> "#" "c" "l" ws* // ID
    ws ::= <%> " " // <program>
    ws ::= <%> " " // ws
    ws ::= <%> {10} [registerNewline] // <program>
    ws ::= <%> {10} [registerNewline] // ws
    ws* ::= <%> ws* ws // <program>
    ws* ::= <%> ws* ws // ws
    ws* ::= [ws*] <%> ws // <program>
    ws* ::= [ws*] <%> ws // ws
        <class decl>+ => shift: 52
        "#" => shift: 111
        ws => shift: 105
        <program> => shift: 170
        `class => shift: 364
        <start> => shift: 385
        ws* => shift: 221
        {10} => shift: 25
        " " => shift: 68
        <class decl> => shift: 376
**** STATE 1 ****
    -----------------------

**** STATE 3 ****
    `] ::= "]" ws* <%> // $NT
    `] ::= "]" ws* <%> // <empty bracket pair>
    `] ::= "]" ws* <%> // ID

    ws* ::= ws* <%> ws // $NT
    ws* ::= ws* <%> ws // <empty bracket pair>
    ws* ::= ws* <%> ws // ID
    ws* ::= ws* <%> ws // `)
    ws* ::= ws* <%> ws // ws
    -----------------------

**** STATE 4 ****
    <exp1> ::= [#] `null !<empty bracket pair> <%!<empty bracket pair>> // `[
    <exp1> ::= [#] `null <%> // `%
    <exp1> ::= [#] `null <%> // `)
    <exp1> ::= [#] `null <%> // `*
    <exp1> ::= [#] `null <%> // `+

    <exp1> ::= [#] `null <%> // `=
    <exp1> ::= [#] `null <%> // `>
    <exp1> ::= [#] `null <%> // `]
    -----------------------
        !<empty bracket pair> => move: 155

        <test> => move: 328
**** STATE 5 ****
    `} ::= "}" ws* <!!`else%> // `else
    -----------------------
        `else => reduce: 102
        "#" => reduce: 102
**** STATE 6 ****
    `this ::= "#" "t" "h" !<empty bracket pair> [ws*] <%!<empty bracket pair>> // `[
    `this ::= "#" "t" "h" <%> ws* !<empty bracket pair> // `[
    `this ::= "#" "t" "h" <%> ws* // `%
    `this ::= "#" "t" "h" <%> ws* // `)
    `this ::= "#" "t" "h" <%> ws* // `*
    `this ::= "#" "t" "h" <%> ws* // `+
    `this ::= "#" "t" "h" <%> ws* // `-
    `this ::= "#" "t" "h" <%> ws* // `/
    `this ::= "#" "t" "h" <%> ws* // `;
    `this ::= "#" "t" "h" <%> ws* // `<
    `this ::= "#" "t" "h" <%> ws* // `<=
    `this ::= "#" "t" "h" <%> ws* // `=
    `this ::= "#" "t" "h" <%> ws* // `>
    `this ::= "#" "t" "h" <%> ws* // `]
    `this ::= "#" "t" "h" [ws*] <%> // `%
    `this ::= "#" "t" "h" [ws*] <%> // `)
    `this ::= "#" "t" "h" [ws*] <%> // `*
    `this ::= "#" "t" "h" [ws*] <%> // `+
    `this ::= "#" "t" "h" [ws*] <%> // `-
    `this ::= "#" "t" "h" [ws*] <%> // `/
    `this ::= "#" "t" "h" [ws*] <%> // `;

    `this ::= "#" "t" "h" [ws*] <%> // `<=
    `this ::= "#" "t" "h" [ws*] <%> // `=
    `this ::= "#" "t" "h" [ws*] <%> // `>
    `this ::= "#" "t" "h" [ws*] <%> // `]

    ws ::= <%> " " !<empty bracket pair> // `[
    ws ::= <%> " " // `%

**** STATE 52 ****
    <class decl>+ ::= <class decl>+ <%> <class decl> // $
    <class decl>+ ::= <class decl>+ <%> <class decl> // <class decl>

    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `extends ID `{ <decl in class>* `} // <class decl>
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `extends ID `{ [<decl in class>*] `} // $
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `extends ID `{ [<decl in class>*] `} // <class decl>
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `{ <decl in class>* `} // $
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `{ <decl in class>* `} // <class decl>

    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `{ [<decl in class>*] `} // <class decl>

    letter128 ::= <%> {193..218 225..250} // `%
    letter128 ::= <%> {193..218 225..250} // `)
    letter128 ::= <%> {193..218 225..250} // `*
    letter128 ::= <%> {193..218 225..250} // `+
    letter128 ::= <%> {193..218 225..250} // `-
    letter128 ::= <%> {193..218 225..250} // `/
    letter128 ::= <%> {193..218 225..250} // `;
    letter128 ::= <%> {193..218 225..250} // `<
    letter128 ::= <%> {193..218 225..250} // `<=

        {176..185} => shift: 41
        {"1".."9"} => shift: 72
        STRINGLIT => shift: 100
        letter128 => shift: 108

**** STATE 105 ****
    ws* ::= [ws*] ws <%> // $

        {"1".."9"} => shift: 72

    letter128 ::= <%> {193..218 225..250} // `%
    letter128 ::= <%> {193..218 225..250} // `)
    letter128 ::= <%> {193..218 225..250} // `*
    letter128 ::= <%> {193..218 225..250} // `+
    letter128 ::= <%> {193..218 225..250} // `-
    letter128 ::= <%> {193..218 225..250} // `/
    letter128 ::= <%> {193..218 225..250} // `;
    letter128 ::= <%> {193..218 225..250} // `<
    letter128 ::= <%> {193..218 225..250} // `<=

        {176..185} => shift: 41
        {"1".."9"} => shift: 72
        STRINGLIT => shift: 100
        letter128 => shift: 108
        "-" => shift: 75
        "!" => shift: 273
        INTLIT => shift: 316
